{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1052,"text":"Last year,"},{"time":2739,"text":"three of my family members\nwere gruesomely murdered"},{"time":5270,"text":"in a hate crime."},{"time":8094,"text":"It goes without saying\nthat it's really difficult"},{"time":10452,"text":"for me to be here today,"},{"time":12199,"text":"but my brother Deah,"},{"time":13806,"text":"his wife Yusor,"},{"time":15246,"text":"and her sister Razan"},{"time":16801,"text":"don't give me much of a choice."},{"time":19274,"text":"I'm hopeful that by the end\nof this talk you will make a choice,"},{"time":22687,"text":"and join me in standing up against hate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":26659,"text":"It's December 27, 2014:"},{"time":29770,"text":"the morning of my brother's wedding day."},{"time":32026,"text":"He asks me to come over and comb his hair"},{"time":34114,"text":"in preparation\nfor his wedding photo shoot."},{"time":36614,"text":"A 23-year-old, six-foot-three basketball,\nparticularly Steph Curry, fanatic --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":41971,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":45684,"text":"An American kid in dental school\nready to take on the world."},{"time":49721,"text":"When Deah and Yusor\nhave their first dance,"},{"time":52506,"text":"I see the love in his eyes,"},{"time":54336,"text":"her reciprocated joy,"},{"time":55990,"text":"and my emotions begin to overwhelm me."},{"time":59175,"text":"I move to the back of the hall\nand burst into tears."},{"time":62557,"text":"And the second the song finishes playing,"},{"time":64569,"text":"he beelines towards me,"},{"time":65780,"text":"buries me into his arms"},{"time":67055,"text":"and rocks me back and forth."},{"time":68934,"text":"Even in that moment,"},{"time":70147,"text":"when everything was so distracting,"},{"time":72048,"text":"he was attuned to me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":73925,"text":"He cups my face and says,"},{"time":75780,"text":"\"Suzanne,"},{"time":76984,"text":"I am who I am because of you."},{"time":83179,"text":"Thank you for everything."},{"time":84867,"text":"I love you.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":87180,"text":"About a month later, I'm back home\nin North Carolina for a short visit,"},{"time":90687,"text":"and on the last evening,\nI run upstairs to Deah's room,"},{"time":93422,"text":"eager to find out how he's feeling\nbeing a newly married man."},{"time":96741,"text":"With a big boyish smile he says,"},{"time":99066,"text":"\"I'm so happy. I love her.\nShe's an amazing girl.\""},{"time":103201,"text":"And she is."},{"time":104902,"text":"At just 21, she'd recently\nbeen accepted to join Deah"},{"time":107864,"text":"at UNC dental school."},{"time":109974,"text":"She shared his love for basketball,\nand at her urging,"},{"time":113273,"text":"they started their honeymoon off\nattending their favorite team of the NBA,"},{"time":117220,"text":"the LA Lakers."},{"time":118649,"text":"I mean, check out that form."}]},{"cues":[{"time":120425,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":127233,"text":"I'll never forget that moment\nsitting there with him --"},{"time":130028,"text":"how free he was in his happiness."},{"time":132552,"text":"My littler brother,\na basketball-obsessed kid,"},{"time":135041,"text":"had become and transformed\ninto an accomplished young man."},{"time":139448,"text":"He was at the top\nof his dental school class,"},{"time":141623,"text":"and alongside Yusor and Razan,"},{"time":143224,"text":"was involved in local and international\ncommunity service projects"},{"time":147464,"text":"dedicated to the homeless and refugees,"},{"time":149817,"text":"including a dental relief trip\nthey were planning"},{"time":152128,"text":"for Syrian refugees in Turkey."}]},{"cues":[{"time":154668,"text":"Razan, at just 19,"},{"time":156820,"text":"used her creativity\nas an architectural engineering student"},{"time":159998,"text":"to serve those around her,"},{"time":161713,"text":"making care packages\nfor the local homeless,"},{"time":163984,"text":"among other projects."},{"time":166235,"text":"That is who they were."}]},{"cues":[{"time":169423,"text":"Standing there that night,"},{"time":170687,"text":"I take a deep breath\nand look at Deah and tell him,"},{"time":173652,"text":"\"I have never been more proud of you\nthan I am in this moment.\""},{"time":177575,"text":"He pulls me into his tall frame,"},{"time":179404,"text":"hugs me goodnight,"},{"time":180591,"text":"and I leave the next morning\nwithout waking him"},{"time":182845,"text":"to go back to San Francisco."},{"time":184958,"text":"That is the last time I ever hug him."}]},{"cues":[{"time":190617,"text":"Ten days later, I'm on call\nat San Francisco General Hospital"},{"time":193639,"text":"when I receive a barrage of vague\ntext messages expressing condolences."},{"time":197509,"text":"Confused, I call my father,\nwho calmly intones,"},{"time":200341,"text":"\"There's been a shooting\nin Deah's neighborhood in Chapel Hill."},{"time":203366,"text":"It's on lock-down. That's all we know.\""},{"time":205829,"text":"I hang up and quickly Google,\n\"shooting in Chapel Hill.\""},{"time":209354,"text":"One hit comes up."},{"time":210901,"text":"Quote:"},{"time":212347,"text":"\"Three people were shot\nin the back of the head"},{"time":214632,"text":"and confirmed dead on the scene.\""},{"time":216819,"text":"Something in me just knows."},{"time":218490,"text":"I fling out of my chair and faint\nonto the gritty hospital floor,"},{"time":221634,"text":"wailing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":223419,"text":"I take the first red-eye\nout of San Francisco,"},{"time":225781,"text":"numb and disoriented."},{"time":227443,"text":"I walk into my childhood home\nand faint into my parents' arms,"},{"time":230972,"text":"sobbing."},{"time":232178,"text":"I then run up to Deah's room\nas I did so many times before,"},{"time":235120,"text":"just looking for him,"},{"time":237192,"text":"only to find a void\nthat will never be filled."}]},{"cues":[{"time":243769,"text":"Investigation and autopsy reports\neventually revealed"},{"time":247030,"text":"the sequence of events."},{"time":250069,"text":"Deah had just gotten\noff the bus from class,"},{"time":252800,"text":"Razan was visiting for dinner,"},{"time":254403,"text":"already at home with Yusor."},{"time":256550,"text":"As they began to eat,\nthey heard a knock on the door."},{"time":259408,"text":"When Deah opened it,"},{"time":261460,"text":"their neighbor proceeded\nto fire multiple shots at him."},{"time":266787,"text":"According to 911 calls,"},{"time":268341,"text":"the girls were heard screaming."},{"time":271516,"text":"The man turned towards the kitchen\nand fired a single shot into Yusor's hip,"},{"time":275197,"text":"immobilizing her."},{"time":276371,"text":"He then approached her from behind,"},{"time":278163,"text":"pressed the barrel of his gun\nagainst her head,"},{"time":280432,"text":"and with a single bullet,\nlacerated her midbrain."},{"time":284365,"text":"He then turned towards Razan,\nwho was screaming for her life,"},{"time":287478,"text":"and, execution-style, with a single bullet"},{"time":291927,"text":"to the back of the head,"},{"time":293392,"text":"killed her."},{"time":295754,"text":"On his way out,"},{"time":296929,"text":"he shot Deah one last time --\na bullet in the mouth --"},{"time":300230,"text":"for a total of eight bullets:"},{"time":302105,"text":"two lodged in the head,"},{"time":303983,"text":"two in his chest"},{"time":305518,"text":"and the rest in his extremities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":309377,"text":"Deah, Yusor and Razan were executed"},{"time":311686,"text":"in a place that was meant\nto be safe: their home."},{"time":315821,"text":"For months, this man\nhad been harassing them:"},{"time":318339,"text":"knocking on their door,"},{"time":319768,"text":"brandishing his gun\non a couple of occasions."},{"time":322579,"text":"His Facebook was cluttered\nwith anti-religion posts."},{"time":326634,"text":"Yusor felt particularly threatened by him."},{"time":329947,"text":"As she was moving in,"},{"time":332500,"text":"he told Yusor and her mom\nthat he didn't like the way they looked."},{"time":336863,"text":"In response, Yusor's mom told her\nto be kind to her neighbor,"},{"time":340305,"text":"that as he got to know them,"},{"time":341686,"text":"he'd see them for who they were."},{"time":345280,"text":"I guess we've all become\nso numb to the hatred"},{"time":347820,"text":"that we couldn't have ever imagined\nit turning into fatal violence."}]},{"cues":[{"time":353685,"text":"The man who murdered my brother\nturned himself in to the police"},{"time":356680,"text":"shortly after the murders,"},{"time":358516,"text":"saying he killed three kids,"},{"time":360770,"text":"execution-style,"},{"time":362341,"text":"over a parking dispute."},{"time":365321,"text":"The police issued a premature\npublic statement that morning,"},{"time":368228,"text":"echoing his claims\nwithout bothering to question it"},{"time":370696,"text":"or further investigate."},{"time":372703,"text":"It turns out there was no parking dispute."},{"time":375774,"text":"There was no argument."},{"time":377404,"text":"No violation."},{"time":379197,"text":"But the damage was already done."},{"time":381329,"text":"In a 24-hour media cycle,"},{"time":383406,"text":"the words \"parking dispute\" had already\nbecome the go-to sound bite."}]},{"cues":[{"time":389578,"text":"I sit on my brother's bed\nand remember his words,"},{"time":392763,"text":"the words he gave me\nso freely and with so much love,"},{"time":396026,"text":"\"I am who I am because of you.\""},{"time":398940,"text":"That's what it takes for me\nto climb through my crippling grief"},{"time":401980,"text":"and speak out."},{"time":403161,"text":"I cannot let my family's deaths\nbe diminished to a segment"},{"time":405967,"text":"that is barely discussed on local news."},{"time":408730,"text":"They were murdered by their neighbor\nbecause of their faith,"},{"time":412183,"text":"because of a piece of cloth\nthey chose to don on their heads,"},{"time":415665,"text":"because they were visibly Muslim."}]},{"cues":[{"time":421720,"text":"Some of the rage I felt at the time"},{"time":423443,"text":"was that if roles were reversed,"},{"time":425388,"text":"and an Arab, Muslim\nor Muslim-appearing person"},{"time":429227,"text":"had killed three white American\ncollege students execution-style,"},{"time":434105,"text":"in their home,"},{"time":435285,"text":"what would we have called it?"},{"time":438041,"text":"A terrorist attack."},{"time":440304,"text":"When white men commit\nacts of violence in the US,"},{"time":443499,"text":"they're lone wolves,"},{"time":444743,"text":"mentally ill"},{"time":445957,"text":"or driven by a parking dispute."},{"time":451323,"text":"I know that I have to give\nmy family voice,"},{"time":453935,"text":"and I do the only thing I know how:"},{"time":456155,"text":"I send a Facebook message\nto everyone I know in media."}]},{"cues":[{"time":461253,"text":"A couple of hours later,"},{"time":462728,"text":"in the midst of a chaotic house\noverflowing with friends and family,"},{"time":466546,"text":"our neighbor Neal comes over,\nsits down next to my parents"},{"time":469620,"text":"and asks, \"What can I do?\""},{"time":472933,"text":"Neal had over two decades\nof experience in journalism,"},{"time":476559,"text":"but he makes it clear that he's not\nthere in his capacity as journalist,"},{"time":479988,"text":"but as a neighbor who wants to help."},{"time":482367,"text":"I ask him what he thinks we should do,"},{"time":484232,"text":"given the bombardment\nof local media interview requests."},{"time":487310,"text":"He offers to set up a press conference\nat a local community center."},{"time":493431,"text":"Even now I don't have\nthe words to thank him."},{"time":496649,"text":"\"Just tell me when, and I'll have\nall the news channels present,\" he said."}]},{"cues":[{"time":500870,"text":"He did for us what we\ncould not do for ourselves"},{"time":503162,"text":"in a moment of devastation."},{"time":505737,"text":"I delivered the press statement,"},{"time":507356,"text":"still wearing scrubs\nfrom the previous night."},{"time":509507,"text":"And in under 24 hours from the murders,"},{"time":511542,"text":"I'm on CNN being interviewed\nby Anderson Cooper."},{"time":515030,"text":"The following day, major newspapers --"},{"time":516926,"text":"including the New York Times,\nChicago Tribune --"},{"time":519701,"text":"published stories about Deah,\nYusor and Razan,"},{"time":522356,"text":"allowing us to reclaim the narrative"},{"time":524555,"text":"and call attention the mainstreaming\nof anti-Muslim hatred."}]},{"cues":[{"time":531323,"text":"These days,"},{"time":532515,"text":"it feels like Islamophobia\nis a socially acceptable form of bigotry."},{"time":537987,"text":"We just have to put up with it and smile."},{"time":540919,"text":"The nasty stares,"},{"time":542527,"text":"the palpable fear when boarding a plane,"},{"time":544954,"text":"the random pat downs at airports\nthat happen 99 percent of the time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":550148,"text":"It doesn't stop there."},{"time":552064,"text":"We have politicians reaping political\nand financial gains off our backs."},{"time":556288,"text":"Here in the US,"},{"time":557472,"text":"we have presidential candidates\nlike Donald Trump,"},{"time":559863,"text":"casually calling to register\nAmerican Muslims,"},{"time":562290,"text":"and ban Muslim immigrants and refugees\nfrom entering this country."},{"time":566353,"text":"It is no coincidence that hate crimes rise"},{"time":569101,"text":"in parallel with election cycles."}]},{"cues":[{"time":574748,"text":"Just a couple months ago, Khalid Jabara,"},{"time":577056,"text":"a Lebanese-American Christian,"},{"time":578880,"text":"was murdered in Oklahoma\nby his neighbor --"},{"time":581660,"text":"a man who called him a \"filthy Arab.\""},{"time":584627,"text":"This man was previously jailed\nfor a mere 8 months,"},{"time":587362,"text":"after attempting run over\nKhalid's mother with his car."},{"time":591627,"text":"Chances are you haven't heard\nKhalid's story,"},{"time":594505,"text":"because it didn't make it\nto national news."},{"time":597232,"text":"The least we can do is call it what it is:"},{"time":600029,"text":"a hate crime."},{"time":601369,"text":"The least we can do is talk about it,"},{"time":604184,"text":"because violence and hatred\ndoesn't just happen in a vacuum."}]},{"cues":[{"time":611759,"text":"Not long after coming back to work,"},{"time":613478,"text":"I'm the senior on rounds in the hospital,"},{"time":615480,"text":"when one of my patients\nlooks over at my colleague,"},{"time":618120,"text":"gestures around her face\nand says, \"San Bernardino,\""},{"time":621697,"text":"referencing a recent terrorist attack."},{"time":624596,"text":"Here I am having just lost three\nfamily members to Islamophobia,"},{"time":628184,"text":"having been a vocal advocate\nwithin my program"},{"time":630380,"text":"on how to deal with such microaggressions,"},{"time":632631,"text":"and yet --"},{"time":633814,"text":"silence."},{"time":635535,"text":"I was disheartened."},{"time":637207,"text":"Humiliated."}]},{"cues":[{"time":639413,"text":"Days later rounding on the same patient,"},{"time":641372,"text":"she looks at me and says,"},{"time":642712,"text":"\"Your people are killing\npeople in Los Angeles.\""},{"time":647216,"text":"I look around expectantly."},{"time":649303,"text":"Again:"},{"time":650648,"text":"silence."},{"time":652865,"text":"I realize that yet again,"},{"time":654619,"text":"I have to speak up for myself."},{"time":657800,"text":"I sit on her bed and gently ask her,"},{"time":660308,"text":"\"Have I ever done anything\nbut treat you with respect and kindness?"},{"time":665395,"text":"Have I done anything but give\nyou compassionate care?\""},{"time":669143,"text":"She looks down and realizes\nwhat she said was wrong,"},{"time":671602,"text":"and in front of the entire team,"},{"time":673361,"text":"she apologizes and says,"},{"time":674901,"text":"\"I should know better.\nI'm Mexican-American."},{"time":677511,"text":"I receive this kind\nof treatment all the time.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":683339,"text":"Many of us experience\nmicroaggressions on a daily basis."},{"time":687156,"text":"Odds are you may have experienced it,"},{"time":689525,"text":"whether for your race,"},{"time":690948,"text":"gender,"},{"time":692123,"text":"sexuality"},{"time":693298,"text":"or religious beliefs."},{"time":694731,"text":"We've all been in situations\nwhere we've witnessed something wrong"},{"time":697888,"text":"and didn't speak up."},{"time":699172,"text":"Maybe we weren't equipped\nwith the tools to respond in the moment."},{"time":702853,"text":"Maybe we weren't even aware\nof our own implicit biases."},{"time":707466,"text":"We can all agree that bigotry\nis unacceptable,"},{"time":710609,"text":"but when we see it,"},{"time":711838,"text":"we're silent,"},{"time":713029,"text":"because it makes us uncomfortable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":715834,"text":"But stepping right into that discomfort"},{"time":718012,"text":"means you are also stepping\ninto the ally zone."},{"time":721472,"text":"There may be over three million\nMuslims in America."},{"time":724672,"text":"That's still just one percent\nof the total population."},{"time":728966,"text":"Martin Luther King once said,"},{"time":730591,"text":"\"In the end,"},{"time":731955,"text":"we will remember not\nthe words of our enemies,"},{"time":735098,"text":"but the silence of our friends.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":741650,"text":"So what made my neighbor\nNeal's allyship so profound?"},{"time":745313,"text":"A couple of things."},{"time":747170,"text":"He was there as a neighbor who cared,"},{"time":749351,"text":"but he was also bringing in\nhis professional expertise and resources"},{"time":752567,"text":"when the moment called for it."},{"time":754926,"text":"Others have done the same."},{"time":757113,"text":"Larycia Hawkins drew on her platform"},{"time":759598,"text":"as the first tenured African-American\nprofessor at Wheaton College"},{"time":763110,"text":"to wear a hijab in solidarity"},{"time":764788,"text":"with Muslim women who face\ndiscrimination every day."},{"time":768070,"text":"As a result, she lost her job."},{"time":771821,"text":"Within a month,"},{"time":772995,"text":"she joined the faculty\nat the University of Virginia,"},{"time":775542,"text":"where she now works on pluralism,\nrace, faith and culture."}]},{"cues":[{"time":780562,"text":"Reddit cofounder, Alexis Ohanian,"},{"time":782946,"text":"demonstrated that not all active\nallyship needs to be so serious."},{"time":787057,"text":"He stepped up to support\na 15-year-old Muslim girl's mission"},{"time":789957,"text":"to introduce a hijab emoji."}]},{"cues":[{"time":792028,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":794035,"text":"It's a simple gesture,"},{"time":795648,"text":"but it has a significant\nsubconscious impact"},{"time":798209,"text":"on normalizing and humanizing Muslims,"},{"time":801472,"text":"including the community\nas a part of an \"us\""},{"time":804141,"text":"instead of an \"other.\""},{"time":807352,"text":"The editor in chief\nof Women's Running magazine"},{"time":809693,"text":"just put the first hijabi to ever be\non the cover of a US fitness magazine."},{"time":815001,"text":"These are all very different examples"},{"time":816787,"text":"of people who drew upon\ntheir platforms and resources"},{"time":819766,"text":"in academia, tech and media,"},{"time":822123,"text":"to actively express their allyship."}]},{"cues":[{"time":825839,"text":"What resources and expertise\ndo you bring to the table?"},{"time":829589,"text":"Are you willing to step\ninto your discomfort"},{"time":831689,"text":"and speak up when you witness\nhateful bigotry?"},{"time":834826,"text":"Will you be Neal?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":837258,"text":"Many neighbors appeared in this story."},{"time":839576,"text":"And you, in your respective communities,\nall have a Muslim neighbor,"},{"time":843368,"text":"colleague"},{"time":844545,"text":"or friend your child plays with at school."},{"time":846900,"text":"Reach out to them."},{"time":848392,"text":"Let them know you stand\nwith them in solidarity."},{"time":851332,"text":"It may feel really small,"},{"time":852748,"text":"but I promise you it makes a difference."}]},{"cues":[{"time":857268,"text":"Nothing will ever bring back\nDeah, Yusor and Razan."},{"time":861723,"text":"But when we raise our collective voices,"},{"time":864094,"text":"that is when we stop the hate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":866350,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":867536,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}